origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
[['ESGReportSearch.find_sustainability_reports', {'name': 'ESGReportSearch.find_sustainability_reports', 'description': 'This function searches for sustainability reports based on the company name.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'companyName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the company for which to find sustainability reports.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'reports', 'description': 'A list of up to three matching sustainability reports, each with an ID and publication date.'}]}], ['ESGReportAnalysis.analyze_ESG_metrics', {'name': 'ESGReportAnalysis.analyze_ESG_metrics', 'description': 'This function analyzes ESG metrics from a specific sustainability report given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'reportId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the sustainability report.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'analysis', 'description': 'An analysis of the ESG metrics, including environmental impact, social responsibility, and governance practices.'}]}], ['StockDataRetrieval.get_stock_data', {'name': 'StockDataRetrieval.get_stock_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves stock data for a company over a specified duration.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'companyId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the company.'}, {'name': 'duration', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The duration for which to retrieve stock data, e.g., 1 year, 6 months.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'stockData', 'description': 'Historical stock data for the company over the specified duration.'}]}], ['SustainabilityAssessment.generate_assessment_report', {'name': 'SustainabilityAssessment.generate_assessment_report', 'description': 'This function generates a sustainability assessment report based on ESG analysis and stock data.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'reportId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the sustainability report.'}, {'name': 'stockData', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'Historical stock data for the company.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'assessmentReport', 'description': 'A comprehensive sustainability assessment report.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `ESGReportSearch.find_sustainability_reports` 并传入 `companyName`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "ESGReportSearch.find_sustainability_reports",
    "args": "{'companyName': 'GreenEnergyCorp'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
